    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index within 9.3% of experimental measurements across all operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Six factors are not assessed per MRL 2 scoping, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 guidance. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
